<div><head>梁氏三禮圖</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.2">皮弁<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.3">皮縫十二。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.4">《聶崇義‧三禮圖》卷一引梁正張鎰。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.5">童子之服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.6">《聶圖》卷三梁正修阮鄭等圖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-1a.7">以童子之服繫冤弁之末。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.2">太古冠<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.3">師說不同今傳疏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.4">二冠之象，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.5">又下有進賢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.6">皆云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.7">古之緇布冠之遺象。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-2a.8">《聶圖》卷三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.2">笄<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.3">士以骨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.4">大夫以象。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.5">同上引梁氏阮氏圖。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-3a.6">匴<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.2">匴形方。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.3">聶圖舊圖畫而圓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.4">梁正改而方。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.5">委貌。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.6">聶圖梁正因阮氏之本而圖委貌與前三法刑制又殊<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-4a.7">章甫<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.2">章甫亦名冔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.3">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.4">笙<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.5">意疑古之竽笙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.6">與今世竽笙不同。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-5a.7">《聶圖》卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.2">旂<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.3">旂首為金龍頭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.4">聶圖卷九引阮氏梁正等圖。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.5">蒼璧<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.6">禮天圭璧長九寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-6a.7">聶圖卷二十引鄭元阮諶梁正等圖。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.2">璋瓚<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.3">三璋之勺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.4">鼻為獐犬之首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.5">其柄則畫為雛尾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.6">皆不盈寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.7">聶圖卷廾一引阮氏梁正。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-7a.8">柶<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.2">柶長尺㯿博，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.3">二寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.4">聶圖卷十三引舊圖柶長尺㯿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.5">博三寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.6">注云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.7">本又作二寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.8">又云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.9">案梁阮二氏不辨醴鉶二柶則所引博三寸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.10">阮氏舊圖本又作二寸者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.11">梁氏圖也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-8a.12">據補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.2">匜<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.3">匜受一斗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.4">流長六寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.5">漆赤中。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.6">諸侯以象飾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.7">天子以黃金飾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.8">皆畫赤雲氣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-9a.9">聶圖卷十三引梁正阮氏圖。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.2">象尊<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.3">畫象飾尊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.4">聶圖卷十四引梁正阮氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.5">爵<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.6">爵尾長六寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.7">博二寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.8">傅翼方足，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.9">漆赤中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.10">畫赤雲氣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-10a.11">同上引梁正阮氏圖<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.2">桁<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.3">桁制若今之几，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.4">狹而長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.5">以承藏具。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1118_CHANT_001-11a.6">《聶圖》卷十八引阮氏梁正等圖<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
